{"type": "article", "id": 25143, "title": "带有年轮图案的咖啡包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-08T07:02:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 63, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702130831mDKHsTUz2Rk1W4bh.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是美国一家咖啡店 The Pacific 的包装设计，设计方 KL Grafik 使用了树的年轮图案。纹路细密复杂，在深色的背景下是曲折的白色线条，有点像指纹印上去的。这个图形成为核心元素放在水杯和包装上，与白色的背景作对比，有点残缺的美感。设计师想要表现出这家咖啡源于自然的特征，但用黑白色的纹路本身会显得非常独特。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130829okRFdP7UGDxbhLpf.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021308296ftvZ12jezpOJhTg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130829RenGbHj9IxYwJoy5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130830yoVSlOgZWz0vM3I2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}